==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: does not seek merit, only seeks a lack of errors
===Idiom===
{{cmn-idiom|t|pin=bù qiú yŏu gōng, dàn qiú wú guò|pint=bu4qiu2you3gong1dan4qiu2wu2guo4|tra=不求有功，但求無過|sim=不求有功，但求无过|rs=一03}}
# (somebody who) does not try to accomplish anything, but rather avoids doing things that would end up in his making a mistake and getting yelled at by others; color inside the lines; a complacent attitude
#* '''2005:''' 张志军 ''ed.'' (Zhang Zhijun), ''[http://book.hr.com.cn/content/105729.htm 小公司如何长大：创立品牌的艺术]'' (How small companies grow large: the art of creating a brand)
